@startuml

title 自动路由安装时序图（probe -> online/offline）

autonumber
actor User
participant "opencode" as OC
participant "Auto Router Skill" as SK
participant "MCP Tools" as TOOL
participant "PackageManagerControlPlane" as CP
participant "Local Stage Script" as STAGE
participant "package-manager binary" as BIN
participant "install_state" as STATE

User -> OC: 安装 DevKit-Porting-Advisor，并返回每个阶段结果
OC -> SK: 触发自动路由 skill
SK -> TOOL: pm_probe_network(product)
TOOL -> CP: probe_network_for_product()
CP --> TOOL: recommended_mode
TOOL --> SK: mode

alt recommended_mode = online
  SK -> TOOL: pm_skill_install_guarded(product)
  TOOL -> CP: install_with_guardrails()
  CP -> CP: health + list + dry-run
  CP -> BIN: run install
  BIN -> STATE: update
  CP --> TOOL: phases
  SK -> TOOL: pm_status(product)
  TOOL --> OC: success summary
else recommended_mode = offline
  SK -> TOOL: pm_offline_manifest(product)
  TOOL --> SK: manifest
  SK -> STAGE: local download + upload artifacts
  STAGE --> SK: upload result
  SK -> TOOL: pm_check_offline_artifacts(product)
  TOOL --> SK: ready_for_offline_install
  SK -> TOOL: pm_skill_install_guarded(product)
  TOOL -> CP: install_with_guardrails()
  CP -> BIN: run install (offline artifacts hit)
  BIN -> STATE: update
  SK -> TOOL: pm_status(product)
  TOOL --> OC: success summary
end

OC --> User: 分阶段结果（含 executed branch）

@enduml
